Chavez Says He’Ll Probably Begin Fourth Chemo Round Sept. 18

-- B y   C h a r l i e   D e v e r e u x
-- 
2011-09-16T17:21:43Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-16/chavez-says-he-ll-probably-begin-fourth-chemo-round-sept-18.html
Venezuelan President  Hugo Chavez 
said he’ll probably begin a fourth round of chemotherapy on
September 18 to treat an undisclosed form of cancer.  Chavez, speaking via telephone on state television, said he
had undergone various tests today to assess his health.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Charlie Devereux at 
 cdevereux3@bloomberg.net  